narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes - you learn a lot about the subcontinent. It was a weird class because it was a lecture and only had 5 students...
Interesting class on a area that people don't often take classes on. I was very satisfied with what i have learned
A detailed examination of modern south asia with a thorough consideration of major historiographical issues-- not encumbered by post-colonial theory or an overt political agenda
I would highly recommended if you are interested in how the Indian subcontinent became what is today.
